com.socialize.ui
Interface SocializeActivityLifecycleListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultSocializeActivityLifecycleListener
public interface SocializeActivityLifecycleListener

Allows developers to incercept activity lifecycle events for the base class used by all Socialize activities.

Author:
Jason Polites
See Also:
DefaultSocializeActivityLifecycleListener
